  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Twas the night before <a href="https://twitter.com/makerfaire" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1578141"><s>@</s><b><strong>makerfaire</strong></b></a> and all throughout the bay, makers are prepping/soldering/printing/fixing what they'll show the next day!</p>
